{"tid":220461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家樂經理徒手捉老鼠","createTime":"2017-04-28T03:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T05:42:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bdfe980637d8cdbe36f627382cb3d356c48be71","tid":220461,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20004432&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20004432%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170428&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=43214333\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20004432%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170428&h=a627d789\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20004432&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170428</a><br />\n<br />\n大家樂經理徒手捉老鼠<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一隻老鼠昨午在眾目睽睽下，於尖沙嘴一間大家樂分店內四處遊走，嚇到食客驚呼狂叫，職員出動掃帚驅趕不遂，老鼠以為可以橫行無忌之際，一隻閃電手在迅雷不及掩耳間將牠擒住，捉鼠高手正是該店的經理，徒手捉鼠一幕贏得食客激讚。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n老鼠（箭嘴示）乍現嚇煞食客，經理捉到老鼠後放入膠袋（右圖）。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n「手掌咁大」牆角亂竄<br />\n<br />\n現場為加連威老道希爾頓中心大家樂分店，目擊者郭小姐稱，昨日下午1時15分，她與同事到希爾頓中心地庫的大家樂午膳，突然發現對面同事的椅背有老鼠「行來行去」，嚇得失聲驚叫。<br />\n一名男經理和一名女職員走來查看，當時「隻老鼠卡住喺牆身裝飾與椅背之間」，職員慢慢移開椅子，老鼠隨即跳落地下竄走。「手掌咁大，好得人驚呀！」郭小姐指該隻老鼠在牆角亂竄，女職員拿着掃帚追打，但老鼠走得太快，並未奏效。<br />\n男經理冷靜地戴上手套步步逼近，當老鼠再次走到牆角之際，他用膠袋套上手之後突然出手，閃電間即手到拿來。郭說：「好勇呀！好似唔係第一次捉！」郭認為分店經理反應迅速，贏得食客歡呼大讚專業。<br />\n大家樂發言人對事件表示關注，公司有嚴謹措施與指引，每分店亦有聘請專業防蟲公司定期防蟲滅蟲。公司得悉事件後，已與防蟲公司商討進一步加強措施，以確保分店衞生達到集團既定標準。<br />\n■記者：徐雲庭"},{"pid":"791a3d01fa04dab31dd5621074215d9517776558","tid":220461,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:16:09.000Z","msg":"老鼠（箭嘴示）乍現嚇煞食客，經理捉到老鼠後放入膠袋（右圖）。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170428/large/a0902a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170428%2Flarge%2Fa0902a.jpg&h=a17f30a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca5ecf1006df557cf8fd83212b49332fcf769f84","tid":220461,"uid":10194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac85f1c6722ad800468002757b56139ed811444f","tid":220461,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日練"},{"pid":"0be2e3325cfd1d4d923f65f2bb2bd101888e4f2c","tid":220461,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:21:51.000Z","msg":"宜家做經理連老鼠都要識捉&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ba1be38bb48aa3d47015b1179271e23e0fb735","tid":220461,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:26:54.000Z","msg":"希爾頓中心喺沙田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fad2def0ff63e6af1a1858584bfe3606c59fcea","tid":220461,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:29:23.000Z","msg":"老鼠真係堅核突 又會咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04c90514ebf43ac50d33ac182ad08fe1b8fb996","tid":220461,"uid":20943,"